1
00:00:02,887 --> 00:00:07,899
♪Do you know, our fingertips
are bound by one string♪

2
00:00:07,900 --> 00:00:12,499
♪Tied to an attachment
that blooms only to fade♪

3
00:00:12,500 --> 00:00:13,999
♪By your side once♪

4
00:00:14,000 --> 00:00:17,074
♪I laughed with the world
wild and free♪

5
00:00:17,075 --> 00:00:21,049
♪Yet now there's no one
to carry the story on♪

6
00:00:21,050 --> 00:00:25,970
♪Do you know you are the one string
woven through my fate♪

7
00:00:25,987 --> 00:00:30,699
♪Coiled through the years,
where longing sharpens into pain's line♪

8
00:00:30,700 --> 00:00:35,261
♪If love is meant to fall
more wretched the fiercer its flight♪

9
00:00:35,262 --> 00:00:40,445
♪Yet I still came to answer your call♪

10
00:00:40,725 --> 00:00:43,086
=Shall We Dance=

11
00:00:43,087 --> 00:00:46,182
=Episode 16=

12
00:01:09,180 --> 00:01:10,300
Xiao Man.

13
00:01:10,540 --> 00:01:11,400
At yesterday's court,

14
00:01:11,400 --> 00:01:13,980
why did you join the ministers
in pressing me to appoint an Empress?

15
00:01:14,260 --> 00:01:16,740
Has even you chosen
not to stand with me anymore?

16
00:01:20,060 --> 00:01:21,420
I deserve death.

17
00:01:22,860 --> 00:01:23,939
Why are you kneeling?

18
00:01:23,940 --> 00:01:25,460
Have you not knelt enough?

19
00:01:26,260 --> 00:01:27,540
What servant?

20
00:01:28,500 --> 00:01:30,500
Do you truly not understand my heart?

21
00:01:31,580 --> 00:01:33,699
I am unworthy of Your Majesty.

22
00:01:33,700 --> 00:01:34,820
No.

23
00:01:34,900 --> 00:01:36,020
You are worthy.

24
00:01:37,180 --> 00:01:39,340
You are the one most worthy
in all under Heaven.

25
00:01:39,820 --> 00:01:41,300
But Your Majesty

26
00:01:41,900 --> 00:01:44,220
cannot afford to contend
with the Zhen clan.

27
00:01:51,100 --> 00:01:53,780
Your Majesty,
it is time for morning court.

28
00:01:54,180 --> 00:01:55,660
I will wait outside.

29
00:02:17,625 --> 00:02:18,785
Other than you,

30
00:02:19,100 --> 00:02:20,660
I will marry no one.

31
00:02:22,500 --> 00:02:23,940
I heard

32
00:02:24,300 --> 00:02:25,860
the Grand Princess's words.

33
00:02:29,180 --> 00:02:31,340
Your Majesty cannot reopen my case,

34
00:02:31,940 --> 00:02:33,140
I understand.

35
00:02:35,060 --> 00:02:36,900
I cannot move
against Xiang Gu right now.

36
00:02:37,400 --> 00:02:40,320
His remaining influence still endures.
The army's loyalty still lies with him.

37
00:02:41,260 --> 00:02:42,729
Now the borders are unsettled.

38
00:02:42,729 --> 00:02:44,640
It is a time of troubles
within and threats without.

39
00:02:44,640 --> 00:02:45,940
If I move against him,

40
00:02:46,660 --> 00:02:48,980
what will happen
to the people of Great Qian?

41
00:02:50,950 --> 00:02:52,630
You cannot act for now.

42
00:02:54,900 --> 00:02:56,780
Then when will you be able to act?

43
00:02:59,220 --> 00:03:00,380
I do not know.

44
00:03:02,380 --> 00:03:04,100
Grant me a little more time.

45
00:03:04,540 --> 00:03:05,259
Xiao Man.

46
00:03:05,260 --> 00:03:06,300
Enough.

47
00:03:09,180 --> 00:03:10,580
I understand.

48
00:03:44,160 --> 00:03:45,680
(I cannot move
against Xiang Gu right now.)

49
00:03:45,680 --> 00:03:46,859
(Now the borders are unsettled.)

50
00:03:46,860 --> 00:03:48,800
(It is a time of troubles
within and threats without.)

51
00:03:48,800 --> 00:03:50,140
(If I move against him,)

52
00:03:50,580 --> 00:03:52,900
(what will happen
to the people of Great Qian?)

53
00:03:53,625 --> 00:03:56,419
(My sister, do not speak again
of righting old wrongs)

54
00:03:56,420 --> 00:03:58,260
(or clearing past injustices.)

55
00:03:58,940 --> 00:04:01,420
(It means nothing to the dead.)

56
00:04:01,460 --> 00:04:03,059
(Your father and mother)

57
00:04:03,060 --> 00:04:05,659
(gave their whole lives to Great Qian.)

58
00:04:05,660 --> 00:04:07,420
(And what did they gain in the end?)

59
00:04:10,060 --> 00:04:12,900
(I will not accept such an ending.)

60
00:04:13,100 --> 00:04:15,020
(And neither should you.)

61
00:04:42,940 --> 00:04:45,859
Are you not afraid
I will disappoint you?

62
00:04:45,860 --> 00:04:47,060
I am not afraid.

63
00:04:48,300 --> 00:04:49,659
Other than you,

64
00:04:49,660 --> 00:04:52,100
there is no one else
who can help me do this.

65
00:04:53,620 --> 00:04:55,740
So I can only place my bet

66
00:04:56,340 --> 00:04:58,260
on what stands
between my Emperor and me.

67
00:05:00,300 --> 00:05:02,180
I tell you this.

68
00:05:02,860 --> 00:05:04,220
You have won.

69
00:05:05,100 --> 00:05:06,940
We both have.

70
00:05:13,180 --> 00:05:16,860
So you are no longer angry with me.

71
00:05:17,940 --> 00:05:19,659
As long as our hearts are together,

72
00:05:19,660 --> 00:05:21,380
nothing is impossible.

73
00:05:30,925 --> 00:05:33,420
(Is there truly a way
to have it both ways?)

74
00:05:34,260 --> 00:05:37,140
(To honor the realm
and not fail the one I love.)

75
00:05:51,380 --> 00:05:52,500
Aunt.

76
00:05:53,140 --> 00:05:56,220
Today, I will raise again
the matter of the border defenses.

77
00:05:57,060 --> 00:05:58,540
Please speak, Your Majesty.

78
00:05:58,580 --> 00:06:01,060
I have decided
to review the treasury accounts.

79
00:06:01,100 --> 00:06:02,539
Without my order,

80
00:06:02,540 --> 00:06:04,860
no one may move the treasury silver.

81
00:06:05,220 --> 00:06:08,019
We must raise funds for military pay,

82
00:06:08,020 --> 00:06:11,420
and entrust them to Elder General Xiang
to reinforce the border.

83
00:06:11,940 --> 00:06:13,340
Your Majesty is wise.

84
00:06:14,300 --> 00:06:16,019
If there is any change at the border,

85
00:06:16,020 --> 00:06:17,219
the sooner I act,

86
00:06:17,220 --> 00:06:19,419
the more secure Great Qian will be.

87
00:06:19,420 --> 00:06:20,540
Your Majesty.

88
00:06:20,580 --> 00:06:22,099
According to procedure,

89
00:06:22,100 --> 00:06:23,579
a decision of this importance

90
00:06:23,580 --> 00:06:25,659
must still be issued by imperial edict.

91
00:06:25,660 --> 00:06:27,659
But Your Majesty
has already given a verbal order.

92
00:06:27,660 --> 00:06:29,220
Why would that not suffice?

93
00:06:30,380 --> 00:06:32,099
This matter admits no delay.

94
00:06:32,100 --> 00:06:33,419
Without an edict,

95
00:06:33,420 --> 00:06:36,019
it violates ritual propriety above,
and established rules below.

96
00:06:36,020 --> 00:06:38,340
The Ministry of War
cannot carry it out in stages.

97
00:06:38,420 --> 00:06:40,539
Please wait
until Director Jia has recovered,

98
00:06:40,540 --> 00:06:42,020
then issue the order.

99
00:06:42,500 --> 00:06:44,299
Director Jia has been confined
to bed recently.

100
00:06:44,300 --> 00:06:46,019
Military affairs are
of great consequence.

101
00:06:46,020 --> 00:06:49,100
I ask Your Majesty
and the ministers to reconsider.

102
00:06:51,580 --> 00:06:53,060
An imperial edict is issued.

103
00:06:58,740 --> 00:07:01,700
By the Mandate of Heaven,
the Emperor proclaims,

104
00:07:01,820 --> 00:07:03,139
with unrest at the borders,

105
00:07:03,140 --> 00:07:06,619
after auditing the state treasury,
all military funds are to be mobilized,

106
00:07:06,620 --> 00:07:08,099
and placed under General Xiang Gu.

107
00:07:08,100 --> 00:07:11,280
The Elder General is hereby ordered to
take full charge of reinforcing the borders.

108
00:07:11,280 --> 00:07:14,139
Minister of War, Sun Gong
is to fully cooperate

109
00:07:14,140 --> 00:07:15,580
without fail.

110
00:07:15,660 --> 00:07:16,400
So ordered.

111
00:07:16,400 --> 00:07:18,419
Without the seal
of the Directorate of Ceremonial,

112
00:07:18,420 --> 00:07:20,420
the edict cannot take effect.

113
00:07:21,950 --> 00:07:23,295
(The Emperor's Seal)

114
00:07:26,000 --> 00:07:32,007
(The Emperor's Seal)

115
00:07:32,460 --> 00:07:33,700
Insolent child.

116
00:07:34,580 --> 00:07:37,020
Do you even know what you are doing?

117
00:07:37,260 --> 00:07:40,340
Forging an imperial edict
while I am ill.

118
00:07:40,980 --> 00:07:43,059
Why are you helping the Emperor?

119
00:07:43,060 --> 00:07:44,700
I am not helping the Emperor.

120
00:07:45,420 --> 00:07:48,060
I am carrying out my father's
and mother's final wishes.

121
00:07:48,060 --> 00:07:49,899
Back then, they were willing
to give their lives

122
00:07:49,900 --> 00:07:52,219
to secure years of peace
for the people at the borders.

123
00:07:52,220 --> 00:07:53,419
Uncle, you

124
00:07:53,420 --> 00:07:55,419
colluded with foreign powers
to invade Great Qian.

125
00:07:55,420 --> 00:07:57,500
That is what truly confirms
those false charges,

126
00:07:57,620 --> 00:08:00,659
and runs directly against
what my parents stood for.

127
00:08:00,660 --> 00:08:02,540
Enough. Say no more.

128
00:08:02,860 --> 00:08:03,980
Uncle.

129
00:08:05,620 --> 00:08:08,180
Listen to what she is saying.

130
00:08:08,420 --> 00:08:10,059
You must have been misled

131
00:08:10,060 --> 00:08:11,659
by that Emperor.

132
00:08:11,660 --> 00:08:13,460
I have not lost my clarity.

133
00:08:14,220 --> 00:08:15,019
All these years,

134
00:08:15,020 --> 00:08:17,219
you watched Chu Ying grow up.

135
00:08:17,220 --> 00:08:18,820
He is innocent.

136
00:08:22,400 --> 00:08:23,520
Uncle.

137
00:08:23,980 --> 00:08:26,460
From childhood to now,
I have never begged you for anything.

138
00:08:26,850 --> 00:08:27,970
I beg you now.

139
00:08:28,260 --> 00:08:30,379
For the sake
of our parents' last wishes,

140
00:08:30,380 --> 00:08:33,340
and because Chu Ying is someone
you raised with your own eyes,

141
00:08:33,862 --> 00:08:35,222
stop this.

142
00:08:36,100 --> 00:08:38,979
I believe that even if you succeed,

143
00:08:38,980 --> 00:08:40,980
you will not truly be at peace.

144
00:08:42,500 --> 00:08:44,100
I do not wish for you,

145
00:08:44,300 --> 00:08:45,539
or my brother,

146
00:08:45,540 --> 00:08:47,740
to live your whole lives in regret.

147
00:08:48,740 --> 00:08:49,860
Brother.

148
00:08:50,220 --> 00:08:52,179
Your bond with Sister-in-law is strong.

149
00:08:52,180 --> 00:08:54,100
You will surely
have children in the future.

150
00:08:54,300 --> 00:08:56,739
Must you let hatred continue,

151
00:08:56,740 --> 00:08:58,380
so that your future children

152
00:08:58,580 --> 00:09:00,980
also live their lives in regret?

153
00:09:01,220 --> 00:09:02,500
Children?

154
00:09:03,900 --> 00:09:05,020
The future?

155
00:09:05,620 --> 00:09:08,340
There has long been no future
between the Princess and me.

156
00:09:09,380 --> 00:09:11,700
Because she is a daughter
of the Chu family,

157
00:09:11,900 --> 00:09:14,540
with the blood
of the Chu dynasty in her veins.

158
00:09:15,380 --> 00:09:16,500
Xiao Man.

159
00:09:17,220 --> 00:09:18,219
Every word you have said,

160
00:09:18,220 --> 00:09:19,419
I have thought through

161
00:09:19,420 --> 00:09:21,740
countless times already.

162
00:09:22,060 --> 00:09:23,899
But when the one
who stayed by your side each day

163
00:09:23,900 --> 00:09:26,060
dies before your very eyes,

164
00:09:26,260 --> 00:09:27,860
only then will you understand

165
00:09:28,340 --> 00:09:30,620
that all those feelings
of love and attachment

166
00:09:30,820 --> 00:09:32,740
can be cast aside.

167
00:09:35,180 --> 00:09:38,020
I cast life and death aside long ago.

168
00:09:39,100 --> 00:09:41,020
As for you and the Emperor,

169
00:09:41,740 --> 00:09:43,260
forget it all as well.

170
00:09:47,620 --> 00:09:48,940
Xiao Man.

171
00:09:49,780 --> 00:09:54,260
I understand the pain in your heart.

172
00:09:54,820 --> 00:09:57,099
But your brother is right.

173
00:09:57,100 --> 00:10:00,460
They carry the blood of our enemies.

174
00:10:01,940 --> 00:10:03,980
Remember this well.

175
00:10:05,740 --> 00:10:07,300
Your surname is Zhen.

176
00:10:07,700 --> 00:10:09,659
You are a daughter of the Zhen family,

177
00:10:09,660 --> 00:10:11,940
the daughter of Xiao Congrong!

178
00:10:15,380 --> 00:10:17,820
Vengeance is your fate.

179
00:10:19,420 --> 00:10:23,259
You must kill them all.

180
00:10:23,260 --> 00:10:24,059
Kill!

181
00:10:24,060 --> 00:10:24,699
Kill!

182
00:10:24,700 --> 00:10:25,780
Kill!
